   - View a snapshot:
      ic inspect [--snapshot (default: baseline)] [fact id...]

   - View a diff between two snapshots:
      ic diff [--before (default: baseline)] [--after (default: candidate)]

   - Copy batches from one baseline into another:
      ic apply [--from (default: candidate)] [--into (default: baseline)] [fact id...]
